This file contains instructions for revision updates.

Update from 0.8 to 0.9:

* Check enviroment.ini gadget settings
* CHMOD 777 on /public/media/common/images/tmp
* DELETE /public/images
* DELETE /public/themes
* DELETE /public/lib

Update from 0.9 to 0.9.1

* Remember: Passwords are now stored in bcrypt format and are system specific
* Check for your episodes - They are now releases and episodes related to each other
  The migration could have guessed something wrong while converting!